scratch
-------
product #=> shopping site

desired features
----------------
root
contains input box within a form
user types desired item & can click "add to cart" #=> item added to their cart
displays all user's cart items

Instructions
------------
MODELS
- - - -
no for models/tables for items re: DB storage
instead, use cookies via Rails#session with cart helper method for cart item persistence and display within views

CONTROLLERS
- - - - - -
ApplicationController#cart
return cart items array utilizing rails session

ProductsController
2 app routes:
1. Products#index (root route)
2. Products#add POST products (add to cart)

VIEWS (created per "feature tests" specs)
- - - 
MVP
text box where user enters product name
submit button adds product to their cart
display cart items
